Quoting Documentation/CodingStyle : 
        "Don't put multiple statements on a single line unless you have
         something to hide:
         if (condition) do_this;
           do_something_everytime;
        "
Signed-off-by: Jesper Juhl <juhl-lkml@dif.dk>
